view</a>\n    </label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">NgOptimizedImage 指令的配置对象。包含：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">A configuration object for the NgOptimizedImage directive. Contains:</p>\n\n\n    <p no-translate=\"\"><a href=\"api/common/ImageConfig#description\">查看\"说明\"...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"type-alias-overview\">\n    <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n    type <a href=\"api/common/ImageConfig\" class=\"code-anchor\">ImageConfig</a> = {\n    breakpoints?: number[];\n};\n    </code-example>\n  </section>\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/ImageConfig#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">breakpoints：整数断点数组，用于为响应式图像生成 srcsets。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">breakpoints: An array of integer breakpoints used to generate\nsrcsets for responsive images.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在<a href=\"guide/image-directive\">NgOptimizedImage 指南</a>中了解有关响应式图像配置的更多信息。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Learn more about the responsive image configuration in <a href=\"guide/image-directive\">the NgOptimizedImage\nguide</a>.</p>\n\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/IMAGE_CONFIG\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/ImageConfig#description\n - api/common/ImageConfig#imageconfig\n - guide/image-directive\n - guide/releases#developer-preview\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/ng_optimized_image.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20请简述你的修改...#L123-L144\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/common/src/directives/ng_optimized_image/ng_optimized_image.ts#L123-L144\n-->"}